Description: Bidirectional Google Drive sync for Linux
 A Linux-native bidirectional Google Drive sync solution that runs as a
 background daemon with desktop integration via a system tray icon and
 settings UI. Features include conflict detection and resolution,
 real-time filesystem monitoring, and configurable sync strategies.
